        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Hludouuicus</persName> divina
                        ordinante providentia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus.
                        Cunctis sanum sapientibus liquet, quia quo magis cultibus divinis
                        insistimus, eo amplius superne maiestati reconciliamur. Proinde universorum
                        sancte dei eclesie nostrorumque fidelium presentium scilicet ac futurorum
                        agnoscat unanimitas, quia nos divino afflati instinctu ad honorem et
                        reverentiam tremende ac individue trinitatis sacrosanctum <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1405"
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Cartula #Curtes #Fundi #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Castle #Fines #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Freedman #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries">templum</rs> in <rs key="#Islands">insula,
                                que <placeName ref="#places/1805" key="#Islands #Monasteries">Casa
                                    aurea</placeName> vocitatur</rs></orgName>, fundari et consumari
                        hylari mente precepimus; ubi et almificum beatissimi pontificis et martyris
                        Clementis corpus venerabiliter recondi fecimus; atque in eodem situ
                        famulorum dei cenobium perpetuis temporibus permanendum augustaliter atque
                        liberaliter instituimus, quatenus coadunato illic sub regulari norma
                        religiosorum virorum cetu altissimo deo laudes iugiter inibi votaque
                        resultent. Qua de causa ad maiorem mercedis nostre cumulum ac loci ipsius
                        necessarium supplementum servorumque Christi in ipso degentium seu illic
                        undecumque adventantium perenne subsidium contulimus in iam dicto sancte
                        trinitatis cenobio omnes res nostras, quas conquisivimus per totam
                                <placeName><geogName ref="#estates/1401"
                            >Tusciam</geogName></placeName> a quibusdam hominum hi sunt <persName
                            key="#Chaplain #Deacons"><name ref="Farimundus"
                            >Farimundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> et <rs key="#Chaplain">cappellanus</rs>
                        simulque <persName><name ref="Farao">Farao</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Farulfus">Farulfus</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Farulfus">Farulfi</name></persName>, videlicet
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1464"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >fundo Hisiano</placeName></geogName> et alia <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1465">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >fundo Palme</placeName></geogName> una cum omnibus ad supra scripte
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curti</rs> pertinentes, et quod ipsius Farimundi in
                        parte evenit a suis fratribus, hoc est quinta portione de <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1466"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >fundo Pao</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1467"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >fundo Pantanola</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1468"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >fundo Uenena</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        infra civitate <placeName ref="#places/763">Tuscana</placeName> cum omnibus
                        ad supra scripta quinta portione pertinentes. Donamus et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs> nostram in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Freedman #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#estates/1469"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Freedman #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                                >Suberella</placeName></geogName> cum omni pertinentia vel
                        adiacentia sua, cum <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Freedman">cartulariis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldionibus</rs> libellariis mobilibus et
                        immobilibus, sicut ad nostram tenuimus manum, totum in integrum. Similiter
                        donamus ipsas res, quod <persName key="#Bishops"><name ref="Walpertus"
                                >Walbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> nobis <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">per
                            cartulam delegavit</rs> in territorio Tuscanense, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curte</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Offersio/donatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/1470">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Offersio/donatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                                >fundo Cattiano</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Offersio/donatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/1471"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Offersio/donatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                                >Orta</placeName></geogName> cum servis et ancillis, cum mobilibus
                        et immobilibus, cum omni pertinentia earum. Pari etiam modo donamus <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casas massaritias numero decem</rs>,
                        quas <persName><name ref="Ansebrandus">Asprandus</name></persName> filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Ansebrandus">Asprandi</name></persName> nobis
                        per <rs
                            key="#Cartula #Fiscal_property #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >cartulam</rs> delegavit, quod sunt posite in finibus <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castro</rs> Tuscana, omnia ad supra scriptas massaritias pertinentes,
                        seu et res in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/1455">Pistoriensis</geogName>, quas
                                <persName><name ref="Guichelmus">Guichelmus</name></persName> nobis
                        per <rs
                            key="#Cartula #Fiscal_property #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >cartulam</rs> delegavit, cum omnibus ad easdem res pertinentibus. Verum
                        etiam donamus et omnes res, quas nunc habemus in <placeName
                            ref="#places/1803">Castro felicitatis</placeName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs> nostram in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1474"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >sancto Cerbonio</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs> nostram in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1472">fundo <placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >Carpena</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/1473"><placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                                >Moliano</placeName></geogName>. Nec non et donamus <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curte</rs> nostra in <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/1475">fundo <placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Royal_slave"
                                >Gorgiano, qui vocatur ad sanctum Heliam</placeName></geogName>, in
                            <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/1476">finibus
                            Aprutiensis</geogName>, similiter cum <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et
                            ancillis</rs>, cum mobilibus et immobilibus, omnia, sicut ad nostram
                        tenuimus manum. Que autem cortes et res superius nominatas seu et, quocumque
                        contractu iuste ac legaliter in nostrum ius dominiumque transfuse sunt,
                        omnes dumtaxat iuris nostre per denominata loca cortes cum servis et
                        ancillis atque aldionibus et omnibus, que in his invente fuerint, rebus ac
                        cunctis appendiciis earum iam dicto summe trinitatis cenobio venerabili
                        presentaliter sollempniterque largimur et per huius nostri precepti
                        imperialem auctoritatem irrefragabiliter stabilimus, ut habeant eas atque
                        possideant fruanturque <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >iure quieto ac pacifico</rs> ab hodierno die ac deinceps tam hi, qui
                        presentes sunt, quamque et illi, qui venturi sunt, famuli Christi. Cunctis
                        igitur tam presentibus quam et futuris cognitum sit supra taxatum cenobium
                        habitatoresque ipsius cum universis respicientibus ad ipsum mobilibus et
                        inmobilibus rebus sub nostri <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">mundburdi
                            continuam tuitionem</rs> a nobis iam dudum esse receptum, in tantum, ut
                        omnem ipsius tanquam peculiarissime domus nostre causam pro amore superno,
                        quoadusque spiramus, exequi modis omnibus decreverimus. Post nostrum vero ex
                        hac luce vita disscessum illi soli eiusdem venerandi loci tutelam
                        committimus, ad cuius honorificentiam nostro studio constat exstructus.
                        Quapropter cunctos, qui nobis in imperium pro tempore successuri sunt,
                        imperatores, duces ac principes, primates quoque locorum supra dictorum ac
                        iudices per ipsam trinam et unam maiestatem districte obtestamur et
                        terribiliter adiuramus, ut prenominatum sacratissimum colende trinitatis
                        municipium iuxta huius nostri precepti tenorem ratum ac stabilitum, ut semel
                        ordinavimus, esse permittant; nullam contra leges violentiam deminorantiam
                        vel subtractionem seu invasionem neque etiam quamlibet publicam functionem
                        eidem venerandi loco quocumque in tempore inferre presumant. Et si forte
                        reclamaverint, ad quoscumque eorum querela pervenerit, pro dei summi amore
                        omnem illis iustitiam adimplere non differant. Si quis autem huius nostre
                        institutionis et, quod magis est, divine promulgationis sacrilegus
                        contemptor et temerarius violator extiterit, sciat se incursurum iram ipsius
                        sancte et individue trinitatis atque in tremendo iusti iudicis examine
                        causam nobiscum dicturum, ac per hoc cum Iuda proditore ab apostolico agmine
                        cum impiis ac sacrilegis sequestratus pars illius sit in stagno ignis
                        ardentis et sulphuris. Set ut hec nostre liberalitatis ac pie largitionis
                        seu prefixe institutionis pagina perpetuum obtinere valeat roborem, manus
                        eam nostre annotationis sollemniter insignivimus nostreque bulle inpressione
                        subter confirmari iussimus. Signum manus (M.) domni Ludouuici serenissimi
                        imperatoris. <persName key="#Notary #Priests"><name ref="Giselbertus"
                                >Giselbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ex
                        iussu imperatoris scripsi et subscripsi. Data kalendis septembris,
                        indictione VIIIa; actum <geogName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#estates/139"><placeName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                                ref="#places/342">Olonna</placeName> in curte imperiali</geogName>
                        anno imperii domni Ludouuici serenissimi imperatoris vicesimo quinto deo
                        propitio; feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
